Package hk.edu.hkmu.lib.bookquery

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Config
    This class serves as a collection of constants containing system specific settings.
    PrimoQuery
    This abstract class defines the common variables and methods used by the classes which search over Primo via X-service or via Z39.50.
    PrimoQueryByISBN
    This class accepts ISBN and Volume (optional) and search over Primo via X-service.
    PrimoQueryByNonISBN
    * This class accepts parameters Author, Title, Publisher, Publishing Year, Edition, Volume, and Institute.
    PrimoVEQuery
    This abstract class defines the common variables and methods used by the classes which search over Primo VE's API.
    PrimoVEQueryByISBN
    This class accepts ISBN and Volume (optional) and search over Primo VE API.
    PrimoVEQueryByNonISBN
    * This class accepts parameters Author, Title, Publisher, Publishing Year, Edition, Volume, and Institute.
    Query
    This abstract class defines the common variables and methods used by the classes which search over Primo via X-service or via Z39.50.
    Z3950Query
    An abstract class for Z39.50 query.
    Z3950QueryByISBN
    Z39.50 remote query by ISBN.
    Z3950QueryByISSN
    Z39.50 remote query by ISSN.
    Z3950QueryByNonISBN
    Z39.50 remove query by Author, Title, Publisher, Publishing Year, Edition, Volume, and Institute.
    Z3950QueryBySubject
    Z39.50 remote query by subject keywords.
